+All 3909 tests pass. The core deliverables are correct:
+- `NarrativeSettings` in `settings.py` with all three fields (`bind_host`, `bind_port`, `auth_token`), `NARRATIVE_` prefix, `.env` support
+- Module-level `settings` instance wired into `main.py`
